Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还没到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,突破第一关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来
